data.description: New price and a new roof included! Must see this attractive home on a corner lot, with fenced yard.  The Foyer opens to the living room with fireplace and windows. All tile and laminate wood floors. The dining area & kitchen with 9 ft ceilings gives an open and airy feel.  Many cabinets for storage and counter space, stainless steel Whirlpool range oven, microwave, & French door refrigerator freezer make this kitchen a dream.  The washer & dryer are included also!  Your Smart home with Nest thermostat, security system with cameras, ceiling fans with remotes.  Step out the back door to enjoy the covered patio. HVAC was replaced in 2019. The primary bedroom has lots of light, bath with separate shower, two closets, and is freshly painted.  Move in ready, all we need is you!
